OL,4,Copens new alternative college
OL,6,Fpoet Lemn Sissay has officially opened
OL,7,Fa special college in Manchester, which
OL,8,Fengages with young people who struggle
OL,9,Fwith school.
OL,11,FThe broadcaster officially opened
OL,12,FNavigators College in - telling the
OL,13,Fcollege's first students how
OL,14,Falternative education and one-to-one
OL,15,Fguidance could have helped him as a
OL,16,Fchild.
OL,18,FHe said: "If there was something like
OL,19,Fthis when I was in school... It
OL,20,Fwould've really helped me achieve my
OL,21,Fdreams."
