OL,3,CWigan poet Lemn Sissay officially
OL,4,Copens new alternative college
OL,6,FThe 56-year-old lived with foster
OL,7,Fparents until he was 12, before
OL,8,Fspending the rest of his childhood in
OL,9,Fvarious care homes across .
OL,11,FHe said: "There was a whole set of us
OL,12,Fin the children's homes... who
OL,13,Factually needed this kind of bespoke
OL,14,Fone-to-one attention regarding our
OL,15,Feducation.
OL,17,F"I was lucky to pursue my dreams, but
OL,18,FI know too many people who didn't.
OL,19,FPeople who've passed away, ended up in
OL,20,Fprison, who just feel unsatisfied with
OL,21,Ftheir lives."
