OL,3,CWigan poet Lemn Sissay officially
OL,4,Copens new alternative college
OL,6,FThe college hopes to offer support and
OL,7,Ftechnical qualifications for young
OL,8,Fpeople with poor attendance and
OL,9,Fbehavioural issues.
OL,11,FEach student is given a personal
OL,12,Fmentor, who creates a plan that can
OL,13,Finvolve up to 15 hours of learning a
OL,14,Fweek.
OL,16,FFor 14-year-old Libby Hamilton,
OL,17,Flearning with Navigators has been the
OL,18,Ffirst consistent form of education she
OL,19,Fhas had since she began primary school.
