OL,6,FHer father, Robert, said: "When Libby
OL,7,Fstarted in nursery we always knew
OL,8,Feducation wasn't going to be right for
OL,9,FLibby, she used to always to push away
OL,10,Fand get very emotional.
OL,12,F"When Libby was in year 3 or 4 her
OL,13,Fmental health took a massive dip. It
OL,14,Fgot to the stage where Libby refused
OL,15,Fto go to school, it was just too much
OL,16,Ffor her. She ended up going down a bad
OL,17,Froute.
OL,19,F"She tried jumping out of windows, I'd
OL,20,Fhave to grab her by the ankles.
