OL,6,F"For me as a parent, it emotionally
OL,7,Fbroke me. I was thinking I can't do
OL,8,Fthis to my child."
OL,10,FAs Libby started high school, her
OL,11,Fdifficulties with education only got
OL,12,Fworse. Eventually, she was referred to
OL,13,FNavigators by her school in 2023.
OL,15,FSix months on, Libby is now revising
OL,16,Ffor her GCSE mock exams.
